info.name: Butterscotch Milkshake
info.description: For all those Butterscotch lovers, what else can quench your cravings better than a butterscotch?milkshake. (360 Calories)

info.name: Chocolate Milkshake
info.description: This baby doesn't need to be described. You all know you crave this everyday! (330 Calories)

info.name: Chocolate Truffle Thick Shake
info.description: A dessert so creamy & delicious. The perfect blend of Chocolate Truffle pastry with ice cream! Dessert perfection in a bottle! (620 Calories)

info.name: Death By Chocolate Thick Shake
info.description: A must try for those who love an overdose of chocolate. Loaded with the richness of chocolate & goodness of milk, this bottle screams with flavour! So tempting that you will have hard time resisting. (620 Calories)

info.name: Mango Milkshake
info.description: We present you the king of all fruits, the refreshing mango. Now imagine how delicious it will be when you add a full scoop of fresh ice cream and make a drink out of it. (110 Calories)

info.name: Oreo Brownie Thick Shake
info.description: The perfect snack to drink! This?milkshake?has the goodness of Oreo cookies, decadent brownie & smooth vanilla ice cream! Drink your way to chocolatey happiness! (910 Calories)

info.name: Red Velvet Thick Shake
info.description: An indulgent milkshake that looks just as pretty as it tastes! A blend of Red Velvet pastry with Vanilla ice cream makes this such an irresistible milk shake perfect to share with your loved one! (430 Calories)

info.name: Rose Milkshake
info.description: We bring you the vintage rose?milkshake?which will bring back all the beautiful childhood memories you made while drinking it. (360 Calories)

info.name: Blackforest Jar Cake
info.description: A classic chocolate cake, freshly whipped cream topped with cherries and chocolate shavings giving the jar its rightful glory. The Blackforest Jar cake adds cheer to any day! (330 Calories)

info.name: Blueberry Jar Cake
info.description: A fruity combination of light cake & whipped cream finished off with a delicious Blueberry topping! This super moist jar cake bursts with the distinct Blueberry flavour! (310 Calories)

info.name: Choco Lava Cake
info.description: A small chocolate cake with a soft, gooey center of rich chocolate. This cake is best enjoyed warm with a scoop of vanilla ice cream, creating a perfect balance of rich chocolate and creamy sweetness.

info.name: Chocolate Chip Jar Cake
info.description: Who can resist the combination of a moist chocolate cake & crunchy choco chips? Putting these two irresistible delights together in a jar makes a chocolate-lovers dessert complete! (520 Calories)

info.name: Chocolate Oreo Jar Cake
info.description: Happiness in a jar with the sound of the oreo crunch! The delicious combination of a Chocolate Cake with Oreo cookies is irresistible. A must try for Oreo lovers and others too! (400 Calories)

info.name: Gooey Brownie
info.description: Gooey yet crisp chocolate brownie is a much loved dessert. The perfectly balanced flavours are ideal  for those looking to grab a bite sized dessert after a great meal. (530 Calories)

info.name: Pineapple Jar Cake
info.description: A melt-in-the-mouth cake and slightly tart pineapple make this jar a sure winner. Vanilla sponge, topped with whipped cream and finished with pineapple garnish, this jar will have you asking for more! (330 Calories)

info.name: Red Velvet Jar Cake
info.description: This jar has Red Velvet cake layered with silken whipped cream and a topping of Red Velvet crumbs. A perfect dessert to gift to friends or eat by yourself. (140 Calories)

info.name: Walnut Brownie
info.description: A dense & moist pastry that combines a rich, chocolatey flavor with the nutty crunch of walnut and baked until it has a crispy top and a fudgy center. It is an indulgent treat for chocolate lovers.
